OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FThousands of Coventry City fans will
OL,8,Fbe lining the streets of the city
OL,9,Ftoday, as the club celebrates a long-
OL,10,Fawaited return to the Premier League
OL,11,Fwith a bus parade and music festival.
OL,13,FAn open-top bus parade will begin at
OL,14,Fthe Coventry Building Society Arena at
OL,15,F1pm.
OL,17,FIt will travel through Holbrooks,
OL,18,FWhitmore Park, Keresley, Coundon and
OL,19,FChapelfields, and end at Hearsall
OL,20,FCommon.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FThe city council's website has listed
OL,8,Fthese estimated timings for the route:
OL,10,FPlayers and staff will then travel to
OL,11,Fthe War Memorial Park, where they will
OL,12,Ftake to the stage at 4pm.
OL,14,FThe bus will pass pubs, community hubs
OL,15,Fand residential streets and people
OL,16,Ffrom all across the city are being
OL,17,Fencouraged to gather, celebrate, and
OL,18,Fshare in the moment together.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
