CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FRoads on the route will be closed
OL,8,Fbetween 8am until 9pm today, with
OL,9,Fsections reopened once the parade has
OL,10,Fpassed on.
OL,12,FNo parking will be allowed on the
OL,13,Fparade route.
OL,15,FWatch the route the bus parade will
OL,16,Ftake across the city.
OL,18,FA one-day music festival in War
OL,19,FMemorial Park will then welcome around
OL,20,F50,000 fans from 4pm, as the party
OL,21,Fcontinues into the evening.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
