OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FThe council is reminding the public
OL,8,Fthat there is no on-site parking at
OL,9,Fthe event, except for blue badge
OL,10,Fparking.
OL,12,FThe pick-up and drop-off point for "We
OL,13,FAre Back: Live" will be Grovesnor Road
OL,14,FCar Park.
OL,16,FThe following council-owned car parks
OL,17,Fwill be open and free of charge. All
OL,18,Fare around a 15-minute (a mile) walk
OL,19,Fto the memorial park:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
