FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FThere will also be free on-street
OL,8,Fparking in designated bays in the city
OL,9,Fcentre.
OL,11,FManager Frank Lampard took his side to
OL,12,Fthe top of the Championship table in
OL,13,Fhis first full season in charge at the
OL,14,Fclub, and won Championship Manager of
OL,15,Fthe Season.
OL,17,FHe told ITV News Central he was
OL,18,Fignoring growing promotion "party"
OL,19,Ftalk around Coventry City as the
OL,20,Fseason progressed, insisting his focus
OL,21,Fremained firmly on the job.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,F"People can talk about parties - I
OL,8,Ffocus on the work," he told ITV News
OL,9,FCentral Sports Correspondent Dan
OL,10,FSalisbury-Jones in Coventry City: The
OL,11,FResurrection, a new documentary now
OL,12,Fstreaming on ITVX charting the Sky
OL,13,FBlues' remarkable rise from crisis to
OL,14,Fcontention.
OL,16,FThe documentary charts the resurgence
OL,17,Fof the Sky Blues, from years of
OL,18,Fturmoil to the brink of a return to
OL,19,Fthe big time, under Lampard's
OL,20,Fleadership.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FIt revisits defining moments in
OL,8,FCoventry City's history, including
OL,9,Ftheir famous 1987 FA Cup Final triumph
OL,10,Funder George Curtis and John Sillett.
OL,12,FIt also explores darker chapters -
OL,13,Ffrom financial crises and
OL,14,Fadministration battles to the club's
OL,15,Fcontroversial ground-sharing spell
OL,16,Faway from the city in 2013 - testing
OL,17,Fthe bond between the team and its
OL,18,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1777871034
OL,3,CCoventry City promotion parade as Sky
OL,4,CBlues party ahead of Premier League
OL,5,Creturn
OL,7,FThe programme highlights the revival
OL,8,Fled by Mark Robins, whose tenure
OL,9,Fdelivered a climb back up the English
OL,10,Ffootball pyramid, as well as the
OL,11,Fstabilising ownership of Doug King and
OL,12,Fthe eventual return to their home
OL,13,Fground.
OL,15,F"You've got to celebrate"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
